e\">\t\t\t<span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">hexo-config</span> <span class=\"comment\"># 仅向 hexo-config 分支 push 时触发</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">jobs:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attr\">build:</span> <span class=\"comment\"># job id</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">name:</span> <span class=\"string\">Build</span> <span class=\"string\">and</span> <span class=\"string\">publish</span> <span class=\"comment\"># job 名，不写默认使用 job id</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">runs-on:</span> <span class=\"string\">ubuntu-latest</span> <span class=\"comment\"># 运行环境，可选 ubuntu-latest, ubuntu-18.04, ubuntu-16.04, windows-latest, windows-2019, windows-2016, macOS-latest, macOS-10.14</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">steps:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"attr\">uses:</span> <span class=\"string\">actions/checkout@v1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"attr\">name:</span> <span class=\"string\">Use</span> <span class=\"string\">Node.js</span> <span class=\"number\">10.</span><span class=\"string\">x</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"attr\">uses:</span> <span class=\"string\">actions/setup-node@v1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"attr\">with:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"attr\">node-version:</span> <span class=\"number\">10.</span><span class=\"string\">x</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"attr\">name:</span> <span class=\"string\">Setup</span> <span class=\"string\">hexo</span> <span class=\"string\">env</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"attr\">run:</span> <span class=\"string\">|</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\t\t\t\t\tnpm install hexo-cli -g</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\t\t\t\t\tnpm install</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\t\t\t</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\t\t\t- name: Generate public files</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\t\t\t\trun: |</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\t\t\t\t\thexo clean</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\t\t\t\t\thexo g</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\t\t\t\t\t</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\t\t\t- name: Deploy</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\t\t\t\tenv:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\t\t\t\t\tGH_REF: github.com/Honye/Honye.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\t\t\t\t\tGH_TOKEN: $<span class=\"template-variable\">&#123;&#123; secrets.GH_TOKEN &#125;&#125;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\t\t\t\trun: |</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\t\t\t\t\tgit config --global user.name \"Honye\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">          git config --global user.email \"hongye.jun@qq.com\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">          git clone https://$&#123;GH_REF&#125; .deploy_git</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">          cd .deploy_git</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">          git checkout master</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">          cd ../</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">          mv .deploy_git/.git/ ./public/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">          cd ./public/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">          git add .</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">          git commit -m \"CI built at `date +\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\"`\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">          git push --force --quiet \"https://$&#123;GH_TOKEN&#125;@$&#123;GH_REF&#125;\" master:master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"},{"name":"GitHub","path":"api/tags/GitHub.json"}]}